strings: <voice_0x01000F31><se_high>Accuracy: Could you tell Chambery that it is time to return to the castle?
<voice_0x01000F32><se_low>January: If that bastard hadn't called before, he wouldn't have obtained the magic mirror either...
<voice_0x01000F33><se_low>January: We are really "strange" and think "how fast time flies!"
<voice_0x01000F34><se_def>China: Our pace is currently very slow. Chamelise must return to the castle to get Clavius's magic mirror.
<voice_0x01000F35><se_def>China: If we don't hurry, the double grid can leave the black ruins, and then we will come back.
<voice_0x01000F36><se_high>Accuracy: Do you think Unchamed won the battle of hearts and attempted to steal Argon's heart?
<voice_0x01000F37><se_low>January: Wow, I almost forgot about that! The reason for this stupid action is to get a magic mirror. let's go to the palace
<voice_0x01000F38><se_def>China: Where would you go? I've got to go to the palace, remember?
